    bf:summary [ a bf:Summary ;
            rdfs:label "Thoughtful and helpful, Puta is part instructional guide to sex work part personal manifesto. A writer explores SW as rebellion, exercise of autonomy, financial freedom and personal expression. This issue covers being out to parents, friendships with SWers and the precarity of SW. -- vendor's website"@en ] ;
